Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.88,0:23:14.04,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是呢  Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:17.63,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如今正是时候  Happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.69,0:23:20.76,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}把握住机会
