Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给大家的礼物夏威夷果巧克力已经平安到达了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人听…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.72,0:01:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  还有SOKOICHIGO的手机挂件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在夏威夷也有SOKOICHIGO…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我知错了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.31,0:01:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:51.63,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正准圆简体}夏天的结束(byebye)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的最后一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假就要  结束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业都有  好好做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:03:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  加油  Fight  噢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  快来看  快来看  这片沙滩真是好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊  果然没人在听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连本以为很长的暑假都… 真是光阴似箭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦碰了面  果不其然又转换到了游玩模式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来  第一学期的休学式上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就在一个月后  9月1日再见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:40.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18}9月1日圣樱学园祭网\N直临决战最终更新版本大公开！\N前夜祭活动内容发表！\N新游戏！\N全体学生参加计划开始！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待度好高啊  但只有一个月的时间吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小意思小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本应该是这样的  可…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁说什么小意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己  你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点起来  睡着了会挂的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经这样过了两天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  你们停一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么章鱼是虫字旁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（日语「章鱼」汉字也写作「蛸」）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个算虫子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么青鱼不加鱼字旁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都把青鱼当笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学美？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到件好事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来变换一下房间布局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大跃进！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变了布局的话  一定能万事OK的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这个办法了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把桌子挪个位置什么的就能大跃进了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  你们不觉得这里空出来超不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就风水学来说  α波也喷涌而出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（α波：即Alpha波，8—14赫兹，精神集中时，冥想状态亦是此种状态。\N灵感或自觉敏锐，脑的活动活跃。）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来  一切都能顺利无阻的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也只有这个办法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  小矮人先生你也是这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  是吧  没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点  学美…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前冲～向前冲～…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛  好痛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学…学美坏掉了  怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来  睡着了会挂的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该醒过来的…是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑  快想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把事情推给别人真不像个男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来就是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想办法…小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.97,0:05:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视吗  又无视我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前冲～向前冲～…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明是个大男人还穿着裙子  不害臊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊  不要脱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  你以为这样能赢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起学姐  我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是你给我上了一课才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我说一句行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们忘记了一件很重要的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我说咯  暑假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出局
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  这样下去大家都会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  都会死跷跷的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  所以我提议大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  轮流休息一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在喜欢的地方写上名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来也很麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  快看快看  这间餐厅的东西真的很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖洋洋的真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想去海边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  就是暑假的最后一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过得真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒来之后  我就一个人站在陌生的马路上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在哪里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然拼命找过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却从哪里都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一脸幸福的模样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底梦到什么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么让她再躺一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点睡着了～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这不就是你一直想买的那件T恤嘛  买下了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  用上个月的工资买的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错啊  我也不要读书算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～出社会上班真的很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都像赶庙会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站是圣樱坂站  圣樱坂站到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  应该是这个吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是重新看起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学美最喜欢吃抹茶红豆冰了  她一定会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳子学姐真是一个美人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹茶红豆冰最棒  我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的慰问品  多佳子同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  我看了圣樱网的运营日志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得你们好象一直住在学校的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为谢礼  就让你欣赏一下夏威夷的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的海滩和餐厅…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说  爱{\fnzhunyuan}洸的学生会长大人今天是来侦查的么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:14.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又是我一个人在说话么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  又是我在自说自话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是圣樱网的系统员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有苗头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有苗头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点事想和学美同学谈一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要在这里做一个很大很大的门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为材料是在建材超市统一订购的  稍微便宜了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们预定在那里放置食品摊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:13:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在那边有烤栗子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边是2-C的羽田她们的店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边是1-B的美和的店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有2-D的山本她们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边则是新城她们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广场上还有工藤  渡边还有泽村她们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  你全都记住了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是各个店铺的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得到？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳给我们点了一把火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们每天都很愉快  这都是亏了多佳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再带你逛逛那边  跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合并？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确地说是吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生数不断减少  经营停滞不前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种时代还是这么漫不经心的话  会变成这样也不奇怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是不是保留圣樱的名字之类的细节还没有决定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之圣樱学园将会被我们爱{\fnzhunyuan}洸学园合并吸收掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和圣樱学生会长有私交不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这有什么关系吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我们打算中止学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个正是圣樱学园愚昧的经营的缩影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单纯的一时兴起  只在乎眼前的一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个完全没有意义的庆典
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太突然了  至少等到明年…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们还处在计划阶段  应该没有任何实际损失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大量学生  为了追求更有趣的生活而离开学校的状态下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然选择学生的身份的你们现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举办这种单纯的庆典究竟有什么意义？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个消息预定在九月一日公布
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前请准备好学生会长的发言稿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  这个情报绝对不能外流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上原同学  输入的资料有很明显的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意准确性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:17:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:17:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很久之前就对学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐这个骗子！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗…  骗子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  多佳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没有办法招待你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学美同学你们为什么这么拼命呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是因为很愉快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是要做很多的准备吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话大家看到这个就会很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽真是害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…诶  彻头彻尾无视我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下的话就能一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我有点必须做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹别扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Byebye  多佳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没能看到学美同学脑海中的影像…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里  有着我们学园的学生所唯独做不到的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:20:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许那个答案就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:13.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（今天的营业就此结束  欢迎再次使用）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  是理事长吗？
